headline: Sail the Untouched Wonders of the Antarctic Peninsula and Discover the Distinct Cultures of South America
summary: Princess Cruises has unveiled its new 2026-27 South America and Antarctica season, now open for sale, offering guests epic landscapes and extraordinary adventures—from the birthplace of the tango to the home of playful penguins.

headline: Cunard's new Sea of Glamour exhibition to feature guest stories from around the world in celebration of 185th anniversary
summary: On May 27, the world's most iconic luxury cruise line will showcase untold stories from guests around the world as part of its exciting new Sea of Glamour exhibition celebrating 185 years of Cunard.
